metadata.name: 420 friends #1
metadata.description: 420 friends are 4,200 unique nfts of 18 different cannabis strains, created to raise money in support of people who are still behind bars because of the war on cannabis. we think it's absolutely backwards that we're profiting in this era of legal cannabis while the system has arrested over 15 million people for cannabis-related offenses, with over 40 thousand current cannabis prisoners.
